# M6b: Process UX And Canary

## Outcome

Wire the M6a process runtime into extension/planner surfaces and prove users can diagnose and repair trusted process blockers without granting processes timeline mutation rights.

## Execution Posture

Make process state observable and repairable through host UI. Keep every user action route-scoped, provenance-aware, and compatible with old blocker UI through `detail.specificKind`.

## Scope

IN:
